Source: nexus-mail-package
Section: mail
Priority: optional
Maintainer: NexusMP Development <dev@nexus-mp.local>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10), gcc, libssl-dev
Standards-Version: 4.5.0

Package: nexus-mp-amd64
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusMP - AMD64 IMAP4rev1 Mail Server
 A high-performance IMAP4rev1 mail server implementation for AMD64 architecture.
 Supports IDLE, compression, STARTTLS, and advanced mail management features.

Package: nexus-mta-amd64
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusMTA - AMD64 Mail Transfer Agent
 A lightweight Mail Transfer Agent for AMD64 architecture.
 Handles SMTP queue processing and mail routing.

Package: nexus-smp-amd64
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusSMP - AMD64 SMTP Server
 A robust SMTP server implementation for AMD64 architecture.
 Handles incoming mail submission and routing.

Package: nexus-rmc-amd64
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusRMC - AMD64 Remote Mail Client
 A command-line remote mail client with DKIM/DMARC/SPF support.
 Manages remote mail operations and security checks.
